item.title: CVE-2016-8012|2024-08-06T02:13:21.788Z -- intel -- data%20loss%20prevention%20endpoint%20%28dlpe%29
item.description: Access control vulnerability in Intel Security Data Loss Prevention Endpoint (DLPe) 9.4.200 and 9.3.600 allows authenticated users with Read-Write-Execute permissions to inject hook DLLs into other processes via pages in the target process memory get.
